      <body>Putting any model into form_for won't &quot;just work&quot; anymore. Your model needs to follow the ActiveModel api. I'm guessing extending the model with &quot;ActiveModel::Naming&quot; should fix the issue. So make sure &quot;Global.instance.model_name&quot; works.</body>
      <body-html>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Putting any model into form_for won't &quot;just work&quot; anymore. Your
model needs to follow the ActiveModel api. I'm guessing extending
the model with &quot;ActiveModel::Naming&quot; should fix the issue. So make
sure &quot;Global.instance.model_name&quot; works.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</body-html>
